data.description: Welcome to your dream home. NO HOA!! This meticulously maintained 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom 2 story home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warm and inviting living room, featuring a stunning stacked stone wood burning fireplace and rich hardwood floors that add character and elegance to the space. The separate dining room adjacent to the kitchen creates the perfect space for meals and entertaining. Enter the backyard from the kitchen into an absolute retreat where you'll find a gunite saltwater pool with an in-water sundeck where you can relax listening to your stone waterfall. Insulated vinyl siding has a lifetime warranty, new pool pump in 2022, 2 HVAC units for the home ( one was replaced 5 years ago and the other was replaced 8 years ago).
